{"questionId":"6b1e987d-70b0-4072-9d03-3ebd56371518_5","correctAnswer":"C","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Substitute into the function","content":"With $g(x)=\\tfrac{5}{9}x-\\tfrac{7}{9}$, replace $x$ with $18$: $$g(18)=\\tfrac{5}{9}(18)-\\tfrac{7}{9}.$$"},{"title":"Simplify","content":"$$g(18)=\\tfrac{90}{9}-\\tfrac{7}{9}=\\tfrac{83}{9}.$$ That matches choice <strong>C</strong> — <strong>C</strong> is correct."}]}